unless user.get('is_premium') || customer.has('plan_id')
  .PrivateConnectionCount(
    data-state=(user.get('private_connections_count') >= user.get('private_connections_limit') ? 'exceeded' : 'default')
  )
    h3.Type.Type--size-h3
      | Private block count

      .PrivateConnectionCount__count
        | <span>#{user.get('private_connections_count')}</span> / #{user.get('private_connections_limit')}

    .PrivateConnectionsMeter
      .PrivateConnectionsMeter__fill(
        style="width: #{(user.get('private_connections_count') / user.get('private_connections_limit')) * 100.0}%"
      )

    if user.get('private_connections_count') >= user.get('private_connections_limit')
      p.PrivateConnectionCount__warning.Type
        | You&rsquo;ve reached the 100 block limit for free users.
